{"settings":"{
  
    "workbench.colorTheme": "50 Shades of Purple",
    "editor.inlineSuggest.enabled": true,
    "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
    "editor.fontFamily": "IosevkaTerm Nerd Font",
    "editor.fontLigatures": true,
    "editor.lineHeight": 16,
    "editor.fontWeight": 380,
    "window.titleBarStyle": "custom",
    "files.associations": {
        "*.cs": "csharp"
    },
    "security.workspace.trust.untrustedFiles": "open",
    "vscode-pets.theme": "forest",
    "vscode-pets.petType": "dog",
    "vscode-pets.petSize": "medium",
    "vscode-pets.petColor": "black",
    "powermode.enabled": true,
    "powermode.combo.location": "off",
    "explorer.confirmDragAndDrop": false,
    "editor.codeLensFontFamily": "Cartograph CF Light Italic",
    "terminal.integrated.fontFamily": "Cartograph CF Light Italic",
    "terminal.integrated.fontSize": 14,
    "editor.cursorBlinking": "expand",
    "explorer.confirmDelete": false,
    
    
    "editor.formatOnType": true,
    "vsicons.dontShowNewVersionMessage": true,
    "terminal.integrated.defaultProfile.linux": "zsh",
    "terminal.integrated.cursorBlinking": true,
    "git.autofetch": true,
    "liveServer.settings.donotVerifyTags": true,
    "git.confirmSync": false,
    "eslint.format.enable": true,
    "[typescriptreact]": {
      "editor.defaultFormatter": "esbenp.prettier-vscode"
    },
    "javascript.preferences.quoteStyle": "double",
    "typescript.preferences.quoteStyle": "double",
    "editor.minimap.enabled": false,
    "powermode.shake.enabled": false,
    "synthwave84.disableGlow": true,
    "material-icon-theme.activeIconPack": "vue",
  }"}
